I strayed from the Aug #ywaINQUIRE calendar today to practice a CELEBRATION YOGA in honour of my 365th day of practice!!!  Who knew when I decided to do my first Yoga With Adriene calendar that I would be here today!  

Daily practice has given me solace, focus, comfort, energy, love, accomplishment, clarity and an overall feeling of success in my life.  

Thank you so very much sweet Adriene for giving the world yoga, love, wisdom and dedication - you are a true inspiration - an example of how human beings should exist.

Day 28 Check. 

So i still have flexibility issues, what a surprise. I'm sorry if the last few days I've been venting, but I'm going through some difficult times as I'm trying to improve myself. First off, I'm not a flexible guy-- I think I mentioned that days ago-- and because of that I am having serious problems keeping up with these forms. As I said yesterday, I was hoping by the end of this Yoga Camp, I'd improve but it's day 28 and I feel like I haven't improved at all. So once again, is there something wrong with me? Am I doing something wrong? I don't mean to be a jerk or anything, but I really want to improve, I'm passionate about this because I'm so tired of being just another average guy with no athletic skill and because of that I want to push myself as I promised for the New Years. So I would appreciate a reply, if possible Adriene. And I'm sorry if I seem like a difficult person to deal with.
